Used for the photometry of Cardamone et al. 2010


##############
# Optical WFI

UU38BVRI from WFI 
Filter taken in Taylor et al. 2010
http://www.astro.yale.edu/MUSYC/

-> resample
macro read resample.sm 
resample ecdfs.U38.filt.dat U38.lowres  10
resample ecdfs.U.filt.dat   U.lowres	10
resample ecdfs.B.filt.dat   B.lowres	10
resample ecdfs.V.filt.dat   V.lowres	15
resample ecdfs.R.filt.dat   R.lowres	15
resample ecdfs.I.filt.dat   I.lowres    20 


##############
# Optical CTIO


Filter taken in Taylor et al. 2010
http://www.astro.yale.edu/MUSYC/

-> resample
macro read resample.sm 
resample ecdfs.z.filt.dat z.lowres  20



##############
# NIR CTIO

Filter taken in Taylor et al. 2010
http://www.astro.yale.edu/MUSYC/

-> resample
macro read resample.sm 
mv ecdfs.J.filt.dat J.lowres
resample ecdfs.K.filt.dat K.lowres  30





##############
# NIR NTT

Filter taken in Taylor et al. 2010
http://www.astro.yale.edu/MUSYC/

-> resample
macro read resample.sm 
resample ecdfs.H.filt.dat H.lowres  40



##############
# Medium band Subaru

macro read resample.sm 
resample ecdfs.z.filt.dat z.lowres  20
  
macro read resample.sm 
resample IB445.pb IB445.lowres 5
resample IB550.pb IB550.lowres 10
resample IB598.pb IB598.lowres 10
resample IB651.pb IB651.lowres 7
resample IB797.pb IB797.lowres 10
resample IB856.pb IB856.lowres 15

